{"tid":837380,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[K-POP驚嘆號]  我的死亡戀情。","createTime":"2018-09-26T10:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T13:38:58.000Z","uid":196383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4874b04bd117865109c89dd346a3d939a4276656","tid":837380,"uid":196383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"【 K-POP驚嘆號 】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（必須開圖片來看這個故事。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-You Can Start ....Now.-<br />\n<br />\n-Yes-.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.-Who <br />\n<br />\n...AM<br />\n<br />\nI....?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n......<br />\n.....<br />\n....<br />\n...<br />\n..<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/180548_a7b90862a4b1089ccd1ef44adb6b6e3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F180548_a7b90862a4b1089ccd1ef44adb6b6e3e.png&h=5e130086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我的第一次死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182359_4c08107c90dc3ecc08255436bb3f9294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182359_4c08107c90dc3ecc08255436bb3f9294.jpg&h=42e5cde4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可能會因為可樂，而沒有後代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182656_a1306c667d82b33089e02cb0d02f6782.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182656_a1306c667d82b33089e02cb0d02f6782.gif&h=87795440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我為什麼會死亡...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182056_de6b7fa4025a79b33b6bae18a538de14.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182056_de6b7fa4025a79b33b6bae18a538de14.gif&h=25f2fd16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抱切..我還沒死誒..&nbsp; 🤗令你們失望了。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182021_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182021_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=04756560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我喝著可樂，看著網上的網民寫的東西。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181343_622db6440436b1929904c71323d08535.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181343_622db6440436b1929904c71323d08535.png&h=21ee1dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得，有趣。<br />\n<br />\n因為他們看到的，只是帶上面具的眾人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/182118_521914b3a1010d2139d9e1c72b6155a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F182118_521914b3a1010d2139d9e1c72b6155a9.jpg&h=2402d243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耗了一罐了嗎？還不夠。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181413_4e7c8440b736e13f073ef9977373e0e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181413_4e7c8440b736e13f073ef9977373e0e5.png&h=81559fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再來一罐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181437_557ae1eed1ef5aee9554193a7176babb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181437_557ae1eed1ef5aee9554193a7176babb.png&h=706d95c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30塊錢$_$真貴。。<br />\n<br />\n但誰叫我付得起?&nbsp; swing.&nbsp; 像<strong>哥哥</strong>一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181511_4efd5a81046d8ec9fb42a25f492aed02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181511_4efd5a81046d8ec9fb42a25f492aed02.png&h=6f46cfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n零食50塊錢$_$<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吃零食，心情算不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181537_8f63f9cb853d4779326016211cf7219f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181537_8f63f9cb853d4779326016211cf7219f.png&h=91ff2c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好了。。差不多了。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181600_6c1b7ea87843150efcc0090efb4a9eb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181600_6c1b7ea87843150efcc0090efb4a9eb3.png&h=517dae1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去睡覺了。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n。。<br />\n。。。<br />\n。。。。<br />\n嗯？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181645_8c261cfda9ccd91527d416baa62da31a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181645_8c261cfda9ccd91527d416baa62da31a.png&h=c1c5cf4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我。。做夢了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181710_3e5c71c2695053cc43ada8e4c0981b40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181710_3e5c71c2695053cc43ada8e4c0981b40.png&h=0b367d59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個人..&nbsp; 是誰?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181155_ac43ed4bdebd27949f15e1efa34618e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181155_ac43ed4bdebd27949f15e1efa34618e2.jpg&h=7a32ad16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喂！喂！你别走...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181257_cce048bb2ab9fdc392ff764bf1798599.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181257_cce048bb2ab9fdc392ff764bf1798599.jpg&h=62d90ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你怎麼。。一點反應都沒有?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喂..小姐，我连你的家都跟上来了....你還是一點反應都沒有嗎？真是....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181757_0dab6fe960109559ff3c6302a914eb1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181757_0dab6fe960109559ff3c6302a914eb1e.jpg&h=4d06bf19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181813_cb768b829d8b4bea0bc49713cac21418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181813_cb768b829d8b4bea0bc49713cac21418.jpg&h=be38e15b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是要我看鏡頭嗎....?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(啊啊啊啊啊啊&nbsp; <strong>你們</strong>是誰！？？<br />\n<br />\n為什麼進入我們這一個屋子里！！！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/181920_3010e79947238e0d5335292d590b52e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F181920_3010e79947238e0d5335292d590b52e5.jpg&h=d56a8f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗯?&nbsp; 她居然看到我?????<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不是啊&hellip;我自己一個誒...沒有其他人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她大概......是瘋了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先不管她，這裡是夜晚。。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n她。。睡著了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我很好奇。。。她的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為什麼。。。她把被子蓋著自己?<br />\n<br />\n這就像絲体一樣。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她..是人誒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為什麼。。她的樣子。。。這麼不安?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>喂。。。你醒醒，你是人类吧。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我忍不住了。。。我好像...我也想睡。<br />\n<br />\n我就睡在這裡，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抱著你。。hehe (*^__^*)<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喂！喂喂！！！！<br />\n<br />\n。。啊？<br />\n<br />\n你在做什麼....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啊？ 我怎麼抱著枕頭???&nbsp; 原來是假的！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n討厭。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喂！起来咯！<br />\n<br />\n好啦好啦。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天，要身体捡查。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈，我们一定没事的。<br />\n<br />\n年年都查，没事的。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n结果出来了。。。<br />\n<br />\n怎么样？怎么样？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰亨。。你腰有事吗？<br />\n<br />\n哈？没有啊。<br />\n<br />\n不是。。。&nbsp; 你自己看看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n什么鬼。。。。<br />\n<br />\n肌肉。。。劳痠??????<br />\n<br />\n我练舞太用力了。。嘛。。。哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n没有那么简单，泰亨。如果你再这样，我们公司不可以捧你。。。因為你跳不到舞了。<br />\n<br />\n（為什麼會這樣！！！！！！）<br />\n<br />\n喔&hellip;好吧。我專重公司的確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年后<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰亨，我是醫生。<br />\n<br />\n我知道。<br />\n<br />\n我。。很遺憾地告訴你。。。<br />\n<br />\n你的生育能力，已經。。。<br />\n<br />\n（什麼。。。。你說什麼？？？？？？？）<br />\n<br />\n其實 不是完全沒有。。但是。。<br />\n<br />\n因為你的腰...傷了，而且可樂...煞盡。<br />\n<br />\n所以。。。你彰來。。<br />\n<br />\n你可不可以有小孩。。。<br />\n<br />\n就要看你的。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－The End－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原作者：GoDone台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv1223190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fread%2Fcv1223190&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=88dd6277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv1223190</a>"},{"pid":"c26568bb53fbff30692588ab0951aadfc966d229","tid":837380,"uid":165368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/213856_0562c052b088ce23bacb1d42e1df348c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F213856_0562c052b088ce23bacb1d42e1df348c.jpg&h=f5de0b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}